data.description: Buyer can take title to the property subject to the first mortgage.  Call listing agent for details.  Your new home is less than 10 minutes to downtown Summerville and 15 minutes to I-26 at Exit 199.  This home has a huge partially fenced rear yard that includes a very unique covered outdoor pavilion for backyard grilling or other outdoor activities.  In addition to the formal living room there is a rear addition that can be used as a family room or bedroom.   The kitchen has all new appliances (Less than 1 year old) with an eat-in kitchen pus there is also a formal dining room.  There is no HOA so you can have your boat, RV, etc. in your huge rear yard and a gate to keep them private.  For an acceptable price seller will provide an allowance or install floor covering to Master Bedroom.
